"ℹ Server: ejabberd (mod_mqtt detected)\n"
"\n"
"ejabberd shares XMPP and MQTT authentication.\n"
"You can use your XMPP credentials to connect\n"
"to the MQTT broker on the same domain.\n"
"\n"
"Per-account mode uses these credentials automatically."
msgstr ""

#: plugins/mqtt/src/plugin.vala:1098
msgid ""
"⚠ Server: Prosody (mod_pubsub_mqtt detected)\n"
"\n"
"Prosody's MQTT bridge does NOT support authentication.\n"
"Any client on the network can subscribe to topics.\n"
"\n"
"Recommendations:\n"
"• Restrict MQTT port via firewall\n"
"• Use TLS for encryption\n"
"• Do not publish sensitive data\n"
"\n"
"Topic format: <HOST>/<TYPE>/<NODE>"
msgstr ""
"⚠ Servidor: Prosody (mod_pubsub_mqtt detectado)\n"
"\n"
"El puente MQTT de Prosody NO soporta autenticación.\n"
"Cualquier cliente en la red puede suscribirse a topics.\n"
"\n"
"Recomendaciones:\n"
"• Restringir el puerto MQTT vía cortafuegos\n"
"• Usar TLS para cifrado\n"
"• No publicar datos sensibles\n"
"\n"
"Formato de topics: <HOST>/<TYPE>/<NODE>"

